{"tid":1480750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：任何人不應利用學校作為表達政治訴求場地","createTime":"2019-08-17T12:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T15:37:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":69,"dislike":277,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"2abc34ebe357beea5094530265259d76f39a605b","tid":1480750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:19:46.000Z","msg":"多個組織發起9月開學後罷課，行政長官林鄭月娥聽取教育局局長楊潤雄匯報局方為迎接新學年的準備工作，政務司司長張建宗亦有出席。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥及張建宗了解了教育局、學校和辦學團體，就9月初開課可能出現的交通問題、如何在學校締造和保持和諧共融的環境，以及如何處理罷課等工作。<br />\n  <br />\n政府發言人說，任何人士均不應利用學校，作為表達政治訴求的場地，這不但破壞學校的正常運作，亦令未成年的學生被捲入政治漩渦，失去正常學習的機會。教育局及社會各界希望校園回歸平靜，學生免受干擾。<br />\n<br />\n教育局會聯同有關政府部門，密切監察上學日的交通及公共運輸服務情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475243-20190817.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475243-20190817.htm&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=5cceee77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475243-20190817.htm&h=4b0415b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475243-20190817.htm</a>"},{"pid":"da1ea30f88f2f4f9b9ca2e4a98f60f2edec3f080","tid":1480750,"uid":240362,"like":175,"dislike":0,"score":175,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"政府話不應該,咁我地就好應該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68ac0baca8af8835cb1cdacd7ac9ff200f75a03","tid":1480750,"uid":201604,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"冇錯 罷課去第到集會"},{"pid":"667fb923e2a2475dbf44da2ca9d73bfd96779205","tid":1480750,"uid":82640,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"好撚正<br />\n幾時取消國民教育科？"},{"pid":"12919d292ea55918f22a0927981168ec4e52d5be","tid":1480750,"uid":59654,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"ci