利用學校，作為表達政治訴求的場地，這不但破壞學校的正常運作，亦令未成年的學生被捲入政治漩渦，失去正常學習的機會。教育局及社會各界希望校園回歸平靜，學生免受干擾。<br />\n<br />\n教育局會聯同有關政府部門，密切監察上學日的交通及公共運輸服務情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475243-20190817.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475243-20190817.htm&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=5cceee77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475243-20190817.htm&h=4b0415b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475243-20190817.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"普通高等學校招生全國統一考試<br />\n文科綜合試題共計300分，歷史、地理、思想政治各100分。<br />\n<br />\n反喇反喇！林鄭批評大陸政治洗腦科呀！"},{"pid":"4da7a5fcaa259d804f20cce24015b905bd836567","tid":1480750,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">張建宗: 任何人不應利用學校作為表達政治訴求場地<br />\n醫管局: 任何人不應利用醫院作為表達政治訴求場地<br />\n陳帆: 任何人不應利用大眾運輸作為表達政治訴求場地<br />\n公務員事務局: 任何人不應利用政府機構作為表達政治訴求場地<br />\n公司腦細: 任何人不應利用辦工室作為表達政治訴求場地<br />\n.........................<br />\n<br />\n結論, 睬佢都ON9</span>"},{"pid":"7327243589bc051f0cab5a099c38daea3eb5480a","tid":1480750,"uid":227699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da1ea30f88f2f4f9b9ca2e4a98f60f2edec3f080","tid":1480750,"uid":240362,"like":175,"dislike":0,"score":175,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"政府話不應該,咁我地就好應該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"其次學生罷課係成本最低既抗爭手法.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而抗爭最大得益既就係班學生,因為邊個後生啲就得益大啲.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f378569280b8aa752004c3898175aaae876a495c","tid":1480750,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited