><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8ad73d190542053c8c06e4bac52ca68a554b7f","tid":1480750,"uid":192587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"失去學習機會，我地義教波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738914583e33d8db8e62ec2c8b269c33569b9fa6","tid":1480750,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:21:50.000Z","msg":"毛澤東語錄：<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日<br />\n<br />\n「凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。」<br />\n〈和中央社、掃蕩報、新民報三記者的談話〉，1939年9月16日"},{"pid":"590c782920aed090ff72438320a0685dc4a8aa78","tid":1480750,"uid":291199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb41ae483636cb777da3348659dadbf374669d7d","tid":1480750,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddace777b47b79214ec82c9f235b4097e424645c","tid":1480750,"uid":86270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"學校係學習嘅地方，咁如果罷課引發學生發多嘅思考，點解唔做得?"},{"pid":"a06ab842311ed85f7c966341bac52ad6620d815f","tid":1480750,"uid":38204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"咁五四運動點嚟"},{"pid":"4ad09587510ef088bf663d6f3e948e141a9fa592","tid":1480750,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"54運動呢？"},{"pid":"d5e0bf2d4c0db32d9095835a5735820cb927cfcd","tid":1480750,"uid":183758,"like":0,"di